{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429540/extras/abouthisgame.png?t=1726328694\" /><br><br>Harmonis: The Hand-Made Kingdoms is a minimalist strategy game where your creativity takes center stage. Shape living kingdoms using unique tiles, each contributing to a vibrant and dynamic world. Explore diverse biomes, from lush forests to arid deserts, and uncover hidden secrets as you journey through your handcrafted realms.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429540/extras/gif-tiles.gif?t=1726328694\" /><br><br>In Harmonis, the world is not just a static backdrop. Unlike traditional games, our living kingdoms are inhabited by residents with their own stories and personalities. These characters add life and depth to your creations, influencing the atmosphere and dynamics of your world. Your interactions with the residents will shape the evolution of your kingdoms, making each playthrough unique and engaging.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429540/extras/features.png?t=1726328694\" /><br><br>Unlock new elements to enhance your kingdoms, adding layers of depth and strategy. Each new tile and character brings fresh opportunities and challenges, encouraging you to think creatively and plan meticulously. Whether you\u2019re constructing a bustling village or a tranquil sanctuary, every choice shapes the destiny of your living world!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429540/extras/gif-fireball.gif?t=1726328694\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Champion I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2429540/343cf32e5b52c443b844082b9183dd5c8752e64e.jpg"},{"name":"Champion II","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/242